Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:05.23,Black Signs,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Coffee Shop Hitotose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:07.98,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:10.53,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.49,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, Miss Landlady.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:16.69,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,This letter came for you, from your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.69,0:00:18.84,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:20.49,sign_432_7_180_3003__1_7_5_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,180-3003 \N1-7-5 Kichijoji Minami, \NHigashi Musashimurano, Tokyo \NSakuragi Hinako-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:22.50,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:25.53,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako, are you doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:27.52,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's changed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:30.22,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,When I think of a girl like you who \Ncan't speak becoming an actress,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:31.90,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,it worries me so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:33.46,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:38.64,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,So, to see you acting, \NI'll be coming to visit you soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:42.16,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Coming to... visit soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:44.14,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:46.62,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:50.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:24.99,sign_3357_19_We_ll_Have_a_Tra,Title,0000,0000,0000,,We'll Have a Training Camp
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:30.75,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it... Mom is coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:33.06,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:35.25,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:37.13,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.41,Italics Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's coming to see me act?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:42.65,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get nervous and turn into \Na scarecrow for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:47.43,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even been in any real \Nperformances since the culture festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:48.60,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:52.87,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to let her see me \Nworking in the coffee shop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:54.07,Main Dialogue Top,HinakoBG,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:55.27,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,to give her peace of mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:02:58.99,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a stylish costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.99,Main Dialogue,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Look this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:03.87,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,No way! That'd be even more embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:06.41,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:10.87,Note,Text,0000,0000,0000,,When I looked at the flowerbed at school today, there were some flowers that weren't there yesterday. I wondered if someone had planted them.\N{\c&H0000DD&}I wonder if it looked like this. Or this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:10.87,Note - Copy A3,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The next time I have a sketch assignment in class, I think I'll sketch some flowers from the flowerbed. I wonder if there will be different flowers then. How exciting.\N{\c&H0000DD&}I hope there are sunflowers in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:13.54,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You're working?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.63,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:18.13,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right... See this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:25.76,sign_4751_40_Yokomichi_Street,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Yokomichi Street Shopping District Stamp Rally Event to Be Held \NOur annual Yokomichi Street shopping district stamp rally event will be\N held again this year. We are recruiting local businesses to participate. \NWe welcome new businesses, as well as those who participated\N in previous years! We're awaiting your applications!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:25.76,sign_4751_41_The_Yokonyans_Ar,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Yokonyans Are Rooting for You!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:25.76,sign_4751_42_Yokomichi_Street,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Yokomichi Street Shopping District Restoration Association
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:23.38,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,There's going to be a stamp rally event \Nin the shopping district soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:25.10,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Stamp rally?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:25.76,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:28.77,sign_4934_45_Bakery_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,100)}Bakery
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.11,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:29.63,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Customers visit all the \Nparticipating stores in turn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:32.06,sign_5005_46_Greengrocer_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Greengrocer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:31.37,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like a stamp, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:32.32,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,and get a card stamped at each store.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:37.02,sign_5085_47_Butcher_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1)}Butcher
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:34.60,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:35.49,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Then at the end, prizes are awarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:37.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:41.65,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,And our shop is going to be \Nparticipating this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.18,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,So I was thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:47.76,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,what can we do to bring in lots of customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:51.66,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-In that case, why don't we \Ndo a performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:52.53,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:57.29,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting the Hitotose Troupe \Nto have its first performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:04:01.42,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And it would give my mom \Na chance to see me acting, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:06.05,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, you've been thinking \Nof our troupe that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:09.06,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ah, no, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:13.06,Note,Text,0000,0000,0000,,This month's class goals!\NSleep earlier than usual!\NWake up earlier than usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:13.06,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:16.77,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you're planning, \NI'll write a script for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:20.07,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll help with the props and wardrobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:23.30,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kuu-chan, Mayu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:25.92,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan, you should be in the play, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:28.85,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way! I don't like \Nbeing in the spotlight,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:30.83,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't memorize lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:34.40,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,But you did so well \Nat the culture festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:38.67,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was out of desperation \Nto help Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:42.84,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be perfect \Nfor an angel or child role.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:48.60,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:51.52,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about a doll role?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.23,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that small!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:59.35,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of play should it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:04.13,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I think it should be one both \Nadults and children can enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:06.49,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,How about an adventure story, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:16.11,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The main character is a treasure hunter \Nwho's traveling the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:18.40,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's an awfully large scale...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:19.88,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:22.38,Black Signs,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Cave
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:24.31,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,She wanders into a dungeon,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:26.38,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and enemies try to kill her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:29.01,sign_7826_87_Monster,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:29.01,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Monsters attack her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:32.93,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,...and in the end, the enemy's lair blows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:37.77,sign_7949_90_Script,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Script
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.92,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You want to blow up the shop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:37.77,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play it safe and \Ndo our take on a fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:44.90,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:47.20,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait— whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:46.45,Main Dialogue Top,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.37,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:49.43,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:53.18,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Where will we practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:55.41,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,In the usual park.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:59.14,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,She's being all friendly \Nwith Chiaki-senpai again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:01.34,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,What are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:06.85,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But the park will be \Nreally crowded on the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:08.49,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:11.04,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't we practice in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:13.06,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much furniture, so it's roomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:16.66,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, your room is always so tidy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:19.61,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,And you have lots of \Nstuffed animals in yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:24.69,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,After coming to Tokyo, I got into \Nthe habit of collecting stuffed animals...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.39,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,They're all very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:27.62,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.57,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk about that stuff, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:33.58,sign_9341_112_Merchandise_for_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Merchandise for the new mascot comes out today! \N\NSome of it is seasonal exclusives, \Nso I'll have to go straight over after school. \N\NIt's only available during this season, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:32.16,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Yua-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:36.95,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,The Hitotose Troupe's first performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:39.21,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You should have told me sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:42.15,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a member of the troupe, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:43.30,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:45.71,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We actually just decided to do it yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:48.97,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we practice in \Nthe school's empty classroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:53.54,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,If we say it's for a theater assignment,\N we can get permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:55.81,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You think it'll be that easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:58.05,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:07:00.71,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,The teachers trust me a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:01.90,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.31,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I should've known!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:04.94,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do have your act together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:12.20,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's more like my stock naturally went up \Nas I kept covering for Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:16.20,Note - Copy A3,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HF78882&}I've been curious about the cake shop that opened in front of the station, so I'll buy a cake from there.\NI think I'll buy a cake for Mom, too! I wonder what kind of cake she likes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:16.20,Note,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000DD&}I worked really hard today, so my mom gave me an allowance!\N{\c&HEB8747&}Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:23.18,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,The cast will be you, me, Kuina,\N and Chiaki-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:25.71,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,and Mayu-senpai is making \Nthe props and wardrobe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:26.93,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:29.45,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll take care of the makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:31.59,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And the landlady's going to make flyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.97,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,She likes to draw, she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:37.85,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe she'll do our \Nbackdrops and scenery, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.49,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm writing the script...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:43.56,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll also take care of picking \Na venue for our after-party.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.54,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,We want a restaurant \Nwith good, cheap food, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:47.73,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys prefer Japanese or Western food?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:51.11,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You should put more effort into writing \Nthe script than picking a restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:55.61,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think I'd like to \Nplay a tree or a statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:59.01,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That way, if I turn into a scarecrow,\N Mom won't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:01.54,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the principal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:04.04,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,So for that reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:07.75,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we'd like to borrow the empty \Nclassroom after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:10.08,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Play practice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:11.92,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't for the theater club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.80,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's private.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:16.37,Main Dialogue,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:18.81,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's safe to let \Nyou use it, Nakajima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.56,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It really was easy to get permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.34,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Yua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:25.06,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,What did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.56,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:30.57,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you're planning \Nsomething interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:33.32,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:37.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you had a desk \Nin the faculty office, Ruri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:40.70,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, despite my appearance, \NI am a club advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:43.89,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what is it you're planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:48.58,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, actually, we'll be putting on \Na theater performance at Hitotose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:51.82,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's why you'll be practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:52.84,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:57.51,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just sit idly by knowing \Nyou're practicing theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.85,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be all right if I joined you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What? You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:03.69,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,As the theater club's advisor,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:05.52,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's just part of my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.85,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:09.22,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,On that note,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:12.23,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,let's hold a training camp \Nhere at school this weekend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:14.79,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Training camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:17.86,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Sensei, a training camp \Non such short notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.22,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:25.00,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you like that sort \Nof event, huh, Ruri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.05,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.43,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Packing my things took longer than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:42.01,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you brought a pretty big bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:42.68,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:47.01,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... I brought my pajamas,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:51.14,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,a change of clothes, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:53.19,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I brought lots of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.74,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan and Mayu-chan, \Nyou have big bags, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:58.99,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Mine is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:01.74,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,...all books!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:06.17,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You brought all these\N as references to write a script?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:06.87,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:10.37,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! They're all for reference!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:14.38,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She plans to eat them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:16.38,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:19.64,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I brought my favorite stuffed animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:21.89,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I did, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.26,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:24.14,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:26.89,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,This is shaping up to be \Njust a slumber party...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:33.22,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you guys are too hyped up \Nfor just an overnight training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:39.02,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,All you need is the bare minimum: \Nface wash, toner, moisturizer, and aroma oils.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:42.18,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say those are the things \Nwe'll need the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:45.79,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think is \Nmost important to bring, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:48.74,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Questions like that are common, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:51.17,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Like, what would you take \Nto a deserted island?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:53.62,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'd take a field guide of edible plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:56.05,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's both useful and edible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:58.30,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be useful anymore if you eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:00.51,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'd take a water filter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:01.83,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:04.43,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:09.16,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe food for all the animals \Nthat would come to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:10.45,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:13.19,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Worry about getting food for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.32,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:18.09,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,This classroom is where we'll be\N training all night!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:18.69,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:21.20,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.47,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri-chan, you're already here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:24.97,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:26.48,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:29.25,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I laid out the futons while I waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:32.96,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Wh-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:38.79,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,My parents told me the best part of \Na training camp is the pillow fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:39.34,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:41.59,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:45.60,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,This really is shaping up to be\N just a slumber party...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:49.47,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we begin practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:53.12,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make dinner while \Nyou're all practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:55.11,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:59.81,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't an actress in the Hitotose Troupe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:03.60,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... no, she gets embarrassed easily,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:05.92,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,so she doesn't want to be on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:08.46,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll change \Ninto a maid outfit later...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:12.60,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:14.61,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a cute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:16.98,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,She's a very good dancer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:21.51,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, why don't \Nwe debut her as an idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:26.29,Main Dialogue Top,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Are you having a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:27.89,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I think she'd be even more \Nembarrassed to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.39,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:35.33,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Time to polish my acting skills\N so I can impress Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:39.27,Italics Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan seems even more driven than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:45.20,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Landlady, is the shopping \Ndistrict event very large in scale?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:47.70,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that large.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:54.93,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,But the shop that draws the most customers \Nwill receive a bale of rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:57.04,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:01.01,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You really love to eat, huh, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:01.81,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:04.93,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I fully understand \Nwhere you're coming from!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:23.53,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we end our practice for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:26.91,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... So tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:34.45,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's a training camp, \NI got a bit overzealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:35.53,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Can't go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:39.04,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You two are pathetic, passing out from that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:41.98,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You're still very energetic, Yua-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:47.53,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes! Um, I-I can still \Nkeep going... I mean, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:51.81,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! I'm going to go wash my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:16.20,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:40.91,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's kind of creepy in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:43.17,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,The lights keep flickering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:46.23,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,F-Feels almost like a ghost might pop out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:50.24,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wash up fast and hurry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:04.54,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:07.92,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yua-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:08.68,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.68,0:15:11.61,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost! A French doll ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:13.98,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! A French doll ghost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:15.81,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where?! Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:19.81,Note,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEB8747&}This month's goal: Only 1 cake per day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:19.81,Note - Copy A3,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBA2FE3&}Work:\N{\c&H3088D1&}Tues:\NThurs:\NSat:\N{\c&H79E47A&}Buy the ticket by next Thursday!\N{\c&H0000DD&}Diet = Having to exercise somewhat. In order to continue things you don't like doing, it's important to do what you can every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:23.06,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:29.86,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan, your vegetable curry is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:32.24,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! It's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:34.62,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,My, it is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:40.66,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's your favorite food, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:42.96,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I like all vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:45.69,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The ones we could pick back home \Nwere the best, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:48.38,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Fresh-picked is always better, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:50.05,Main Dialogue,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,What's your favorite, Mayu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:53.75,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I like shortcake and Hamburg steaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:57.78,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I like nanbu senbei, salt-grilled saury...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:59.28,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and plum-and-kelp tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:03.49,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the foods I like are the things\N that you like the least, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:04.32,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:08.19,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You two really are opposite extremes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:15.91,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,The school is kind of creepy \Nat night, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:20.04,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, have you heard of \Nthis school's seven mysteries?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:22.54,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It has those?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:25.17,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Your school didn't have anything \Nlike that, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:27.42,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite interested, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:31.55,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:32.42,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:36.51,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I think there was a walking \NNinomiya Kinjirou,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:39.18,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,a Ninomiya Kinjirou \Nthat suddenly grew heavy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:41.83,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,a dancing Ninomiya Kinjirou,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:43.87,Italics Dialogue Top,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want them to think I, \NYua-sama, was scared by a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:43.91,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,the Ninomiya Kinjirou in the mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:48.06,Italics Dialogue Top,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not leaving this classroom again \Nfor the rest of the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:45.56,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,a stain on the wall that \Nwas Ninomiya Kinjirou,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:48.06,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,a Ninomiya Kinjirou with shining eyes, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:51.36,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:54.63,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, could you go get a washrag \Nfrom the home ec classroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:55.20,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:56.82,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:17:00.33,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I just said that out of habit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:02.77,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you can both go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:03.83,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:14.84,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not scared... I'm not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:20.35,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um, the home ec room is this way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:31.24,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so that's why Mayu-chan gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:36.61,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... W-Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:42.99,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I shouldn't have \Nleft the classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:45.00,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so scared, I feel like I'll pass out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:48.67,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan, do you not like dark places?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:54.69,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,That's not... not... not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:56.26,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you scared, Hinako?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:58.89,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:02.30,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But you always help me out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:05.27,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I should be \Nthere for you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:09.77,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're just Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:14.10,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fine. I guess I'll hold your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:15.53,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.31,0:18:21.16,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is still a lot brighter \Nthan the countryside at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:30.92,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why'd you stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.20,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Something's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:33.92,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:36.59,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.30,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,See? Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:40.98,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's nothing there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:46.56,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Hinako! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:50.64,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hinako?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:52.56,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:02.34,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hinako?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:12.87,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan, look! It was a kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:15.28,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it wandered in here and got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:23.09,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:31.46,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, Kuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:34.80,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't training camps fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:37.36,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could stay over at \Nschool every weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:39.49,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:41.89,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,After spending the day with all of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:44.64,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got some ideas for my script!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:46.16,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,It's a horror story, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.49,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:50.28,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:51.62,Italics Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's having fun, and all is well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:52.34,Main Dialogue Top,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:54.67,Italics Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this kind of training camp \Ncould be nice once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:56.41,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:20:00.72,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,When do we get to have the pillow fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:03.51,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You're really stuck on that, huh, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:06.31,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:17.52,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako, are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:24.42,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's fine if you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:31.64,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Thanks for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:35.54,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,It was really reassuring having you ther—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:42.69,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan?! Yua-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:44.34,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:44.34,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:47.55,Main Dialogue Top,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:47.55,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,A burglar?! Is there a burglar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:57.57,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The training camp was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:20:59.57,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Last night was awful for me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:04.25,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I can't sleep \Nwithout that mask on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:06.68,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like I was scared or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:08.65,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,It just startled me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:12.78,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,"It just startled me."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:16.08,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan, are you writing the script?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:18.96,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! I think it'll be done \Nby the end of this week!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:21.36,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:24.41,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It's not a horror story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.41,0:21:26.47,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}not{\i0} scared of that stuff, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:29.86,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The script and our practices \Nare coming along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:31.27,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep this up,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:34.03,Italics Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can be confident on the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.03,0:21:37.73,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure Mom sees me at my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:40.51,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait until the day of the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.51,0:21:41.11,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:47.11,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make the Hitotose Troupe's \Nfirst performance a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:48.25,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.25,0:21:52.40,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, is a bale of rice \Nthat appealing to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.40,0:21:55.00,Main Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Bale of rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:33.05,sign_33687_382_Pa_Pa_Parade,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,6000)}Pa-Pa-Parade
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.40,0:23:31.79,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan finally finished the script for \Nthe Hitotose Troupe's first performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:34.50,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Which means it's my time to shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.50,0:23:37.39,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, try on these costumes right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.39,0:23:39.46,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Pa-Pa-Parade."
